r \in (x^3, xy) 
r= ax^3+b xy 
r=x(ax^2+by)
r\in (x)
r\in(x^3,xy)\implies r=ax^3+bxy=x(ax^2+by)\implies r\in(x)
r=a(x^3)+(bx)y\implies r\in(x^3,y)
r\in(x)\cap(x^3,y)
(x^3,xy)\subseteq(x)\cap(x^3,y)
r\in(x)\cap(x^3,y)
r=kx=lx^3+my
x(k-lx^2)=my
x\vert my
x\vert m
x\not\mid y
m=nx\implies r=lx^3+nxy=l(x^3)+n(xy)\in(x^3,xy)
